MeuTwitter

Description:
A simple Twitter client for Android for educational use.
Used on talks and trainings.

Author: 
Carlos EugÃªnio Torres <carlos.torres@cacira.com.br>
http://cetorres.com
http://cacira.com.br

Main concepts covered on this project:
* HTTP calls (GET) to the JSON Twitter API
* JSON parsing
* Interface building (widgets, styles, menus, drawables...)
* Listings (ListView, ListAdapter)
* Asyncronous tasks using AsyncTask for async remote data loading
* User preferences (Prefs)
* Android manifest


